@page
@model HealthConnect.Pages.Return_And_RefundModel
@{
    Layout = "_Header";
    ViewData["Title"] = "Return & Refund";
}
<div class="refund-container">
    <div class="refund">
        <h1 class="refund-title">Return & Refund Policy</h1>

        <p class="refund-paragraph">
            Thank you for using Health Connect. We aim to provide you with high-quality healthcare services. If you are not completely satisfied with the services or products you have purchased, we are here to assist you. Please read our Return & Refund Policy carefully to understand your rights and options.
        </p>

        <h2 class="refund-subtitle">1. Doctor Consultation Refunds</h2>
        <p class="refund-paragraph">
            If you are not satisfied with a doctor consultation for any reason, we offer refunds under the following conditions:
        </p>
        <ul class="refund-list">
            <li>✔ Refunds will be processed if the doctor is unavailable or the consultation did not take place due to platform issues.</li>
            <li>✔ Refund requests must be submitted within 24 hours of the scheduled consultation time.</li>
            <li>✔ Refunds are not provided for missed appointments unless there is a valid reason, such as platform downtime or technical difficulties.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="refund-subtitle">2. Pharmacy Order Refunds</h2>
        <p class="refund-paragraph">
            We strive to ensure that your pharmacy orders are delivered as per your prescription. However, in the case of errors or issues with your order, you are eligible for a refund under the following conditions:
        </p>
        <ul class="refund-list">
            <li>✔ Refunds are available if an incorrect item was delivered or if the item is damaged during delivery.</li>
            <li>✔ Refund requests must be made within 7 days from the delivery date.</li>
            <li>✔ To initiate a refund, please contact our support team with details of your order and the issue you encountered.</li>
            <li>✔ Once your refund request is validated, we will process the refund to the original payment method.</li>
            <li>✔ For prescriptions that are incorrectly filled or expired, we will issue a full refund or replace the item at no additional cost to you.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="refund-subtitle">3. Non-Refundable Services</h2>
        <p class="refund-paragraph">
            Some services may be non-refundable. These include:
        </p>
        <ul class="refund-list">
            <li>✔ Fees for consultations that have already taken place.</li>
            <li>✔ Orders for medications that have been opened, used, or are non-returnable for health and safety reasons.</li>
            <li>✔ Digital services, such as consultation fees for services rendered or consumed.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="refund-subtitle">4. How to Request a Refund</h2>
        <p class="refund-paragraph">
            To request a refund, please follow these steps:
        </p>
        <ul class="refund-list">
            <li>✔ Contact our customer support team at <strong>support@healthconnect.com</strong> with your order details and reason for the refund request.</li>
            <li>✔ For consultations, provide the consultation ID, doctor’s name, and the reason for your refund request.</li>
            <li>✔ For pharmacy orders, provide your order number and the reason for your refund request, along with any evidence (such as photographs) of damaged or incorrect items.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="refund-subtitle">5. Processing Refunds</h2>
        <p class="refund-paragraph">
            Once your refund request is reviewed and approved, refunds will be processed as follows:
        </p>
        <ul class="refund-list">
            <li>✔ Refunds for consultations will be processed within 7 business days after approval.</li>
            <li>✔ Refunds for pharmacy orders will be processed within 10 business days after approval, depending on your payment method.</li>
            <li>✔ Refunds will be issued to the original payment method used for the transaction (credit card, debit card, or other payment methods).</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="refund-subtitle">6. Cancellation Policy</h2>
        <p class="refund-paragraph">
            You can cancel a doctor consultation or pharmacy order under the following conditions:
        </p>
        <ul class="refund-list">
            <li>✔ Consultations can be canceled at least 1 hour before the scheduled appointment time for a full refund.</li>
            <li>✔ Pharmacy orders can be canceled before dispatch for a full refund.</li>
            <li>✔ Cancellations must be made by contacting our customer support team in advance.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="refund-subtitle">7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="refund-paragraph">
            If you have any questions regarding our Return & Refund Policy or need assistance with a refund request, please contact us at <strong>healthconnect058@gmail.com</strong>.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
